object.script:
-- Tick function that will be executed every logic tick function onTick() delx = input.getNumber(1) dely = input.getNumber(2) speed = (delx^2+dely^2)^(1/2)*60 HDG = 1 end
-- Draw function that will be executed when this script renders to a screen function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() -- Get the screen's width and height h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(0, 255, 0) -- Set draw color to green
-- screen.drawCircle(w / 2, (h / 2)+5, 15) -- Draw crossair screen.drawLine((w/2)-2,(h/2)+5,(w/2)+3,(h/2)+5) screen.drawLine((w/2),(h/2)+3,(w/2),(h/2)+8)
screen.drawTextBox(0,h-6,w,6,"HDG: ",0,0) screen.drawTextBox(0,h-6,w+30,6,string.format("%3.2f",HDG),0,0)
screen.drawTextBox(0,h/2,w,12,"SOG:",1,-1) screen.drawTextBox(0,h/2,w,12,string.format("%3.2f",speed),1,1) end
